title: What Barack Obama said about UFO files that made Donald Trump say "he made a big mistake"
description: President Trump has ordered the release of government files concerning UFOs and extraterrestrial life, citing immense public interest. This follows former President Obama's remarks on the topic. While the US government acknowledges Unidentified Aerial Phenomena (UAP) are real, reports indicate no confirmed extraterrestrial origins, with many sightings attributed to mundane objects or advanced US technology.
